npx create-react-app in the frontend folder
create index.js in backend folder and npm init -y

in the backend we need the following package
npm i body-parser cors express mongoose nodemon

body-parser helps us to create post request.
cors for cross origin resource sharing
express a node framework which help us with routing and a host of other things
moongoose helps us to create and manage models in our application
nodemon to help automate watch and build process

dependencies for client side application
npm i axios momment react-file-base64 redux redux-thunk

axios for making asynchronous calls
moment for working with date and time
react-file-base64 for uploading images 
redux for state management
redux-thunk for asynchronous actions using redux.






